3300:[name]梨深[line]I'm sure the people who can are very romantic and sensitive.[%p]
3400:[name]将軍[line]I have long, long dreams. All the time.[%p]
3500:[name]将軍[line]They seem to go on for years while I'm dreaming them.[%p]
